            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Another Inspiration </h2>
            <p class="lead">Meet Nandhakumar, a father, son & husband. He is at the market every day, come rain or shine. Very easy to miss, meeting him in the evenings, you will find crates lying empty which housed the goods he sold throughout the day. Help him get access to economical credit and build the house that he was always dreamt of! <br><br>
Help him get out of the grip of these unscrupulous loan sharks!</p>
        </div>

